    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines a new pre-authentication mechanism for the Kerberos protocol.  The mechanism uses a password-authenticated key exchange (PAKE) to prevent brute-force password attacks, and it may incorporate a second factor.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
